32:04.464 --> 32:06.877
No, I'm, no thank you.

32:06.925 --> 32:08.336
Suit yourself.

32:08.385 --> 32:12.379
Fuckin' come on, come up here,
that's right, yes!

32:12.431 --> 32:15.720
Take it, take it up the wrong 'un,
oh God!

32:15.767 --> 32:17.975
