33:13.909 --> 33:16.492
Hang on, I'll just use my X-ray vision
to see through the door.

33:16.536 --> 33:18.653
Sarcasm is the lowest form of wit.

33:22.626 --> 33:25.039
All I'm saying is nothing good
ever happens.

33:25.086 --> 33:27.794
In fact, nothing interesting
ever happens to us.

33:27.839 --> 33:29.796
Sorry to trouble you,
but we need some help.

33:37.557 --> 33:39.469
Fuck.

33:39.518 --> 33:41.510
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

33:41.561 --> 33:44.804
- Oh shit!
- Is he dead?

33:44.856 --> 33:47.314
