46:33.082 --> 46:34.744
Cos he was starin' at me.

46:36.377 --> 46:37.868
Right.

46:37.920 --> 46:39.331
Goodbye, Oz.

46:40.840 --> 46:42.672
Are you okay?

46:45.219 --> 46:47.006
It's strange I...

46:47.054 --> 46:49.296
I don't feel any remorse.

46:52.101 --> 46:53.683
Maybe it'll come later.

46:56.272 --> 46:58.389
Do you, do you think they'll hurt us?

47:00.693 --> 47:02.855
No, not intentionally.

47:05.448 --> 47:07.906
I do think we could be in trouble.

47:07.950 --> 47:11.534
Whoever's after those guys
doesn't care who stands in their way.

47:13.622 --> 47:17.332
