47:45.404 --> 47:46.736
First thing tomorrow.

47:49.158 --> 47:50.399
Hey.

47:51.535 --> 47:53.197
How's your arm?

47:53.245 --> 47:54.827
I'll hold.

47:54.872 --> 47:56.829
That bastard hit me.

47:59.377 --> 48:01.243
Well, you did kill him, to be fair.

48:05.174 --> 48:07.382
